<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbcdb1bc6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s4721"><num value="4721">§ 4721.</num><heading> Declaration of purpose</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purpose of this subchapter is to assist State and local governments to strengthen their staffs by improving their personnel administration.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbcdb1bc7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/648/tII/s201">Pub. L. 91–648, title II, § 201</ref>, <date date="1971-01-05">Jan. 5, 1971</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1911">84 Stat. 1911</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
